snippet.title: Love, Ghostie - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Love, Ghostie will be releasing on August 14, 2024 - wishlist now on Steam!

Become a wholesome ghost matchmaker and grow relationships between the manor’s residents! Gift items to lift their spirits, set them up on dates, and watch love bloom! Discover cute romances with a unique story between every pair of residents! How will love blossom in your manor?

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1789490/Love_Ghostie/?utm_source=youtube
Website: https://www.janbehgames.com/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@janbehchanbeh
